      "name": "觀賞魚",
      "iconUrl": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/tutorial/Ornamental Fish_icon.png"
    },
    {
      "epId": 2644,
      "name": "詭異的「黑泥」…",
      "iconUrl": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/tutorial/The Ominous Dark Mud_icon.png",
      "desc": "處在這種神秘的「黑泥」中時，角色會持續損失生命值，行動能力也會受到影響。「流明石觸媒」中儲存的能量，在這種情況下也會漸漸流失。"
    },
    {
      "epId": 2645,
      "name": "遲滯之水",
      "iconUrl": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/tutorial/Slowing Water_icon.png",
      "desc": "「遲滯之水」狀態會<span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">延長技能冷卻時間</span>。如果能通過<span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">元素反應</span>將角色附著的水元素消除的話，就能解除這種狀態。"
    },
    {
      "epId": 2646,
      "name": "釣魚",
      "iconUrl": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/tutorial/Fishing_icon.png"
    },
    {
